HEADWORD: Phonomotor
<hw>Pho`no*mo"tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Phono-</ets> + <ets>-motor</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Physics)</fld>
